gr.interamerican.bo2.arch.ext
Interface Cache<C extends java.lang.Comparable<? super C>>

Type Parameters:
C - Type of entries code.
public interface Cache<C extends java.lang.Comparable<? super C>>

Cache caches the values of objects used often and changed rare. List elements are the most frequent objects handled by a cache. Cache Objects are uniquely identified by the pair (typeId, code).
